{"tid":681944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖）又有大波港女喺IG搏出位","createTime":"2018-05-28T12:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:38:43.000Z","uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccf8f2d2cfab8a42a21cae04ca0c138f87cf717","tid":681944,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/27/QARBMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2FQARBMx.jpg&h=b4ef36b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n欣宜曾經因身形肥胖而自卑，曾決心減肥，由近230磅減至130磅，原來瘦咗之後，生活仍然唔易過。2014年欣宜喺Facebook表態停止再減肥：「重組自己，開展健康的生活，不會再強迫自己」，並在微博高呼：「我要為肥人爭光！」<br />\r\n今日嘅欣宜真係開心咗好多。欣宜經常喺社交網分享吃喝玩樂嘅相，尤其喜歡show驕人身材，因為有自信嘛，加大碼都可以靚靚。<br />\r\n欣宜噚日喺ig story分享一段佢同女性友人一齊浸spa嘅短片，見佢穿著一件火辣辣嘅紅色比堅尼，側身舉V同朋友一齊影合照，笑得好開心。之後佢仲同呢位女性朋友一齊睇日落，佢話：「「同我女人一齊睇日落，真浪漫！」不過，大家唔好誤會欣宜轉性向，呢位女性朋友係有老公嘅，而欣宜就繼續單身。"},{"pid":"b04714177efebb99c32f58f7b8a045f75df18ca6","tid":681944,"uid":12370,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我要洗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae9ffedf8db581785e74fa4746ae9eeaade692","tid":681944,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14673baf9f7d8c98733a20ff06471532a4af1a74","tid":681944,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8ae096f365561c80b24468126e7ddaf13f1e08","tid":681944,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/204709_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F204709_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=957fb6db&s={SIZE}\"